high_descs: Leave the room. Cross to the right. In front of the desk.
Exit the room, cross to the right. Cross to the right. Reach the refrigerator. Turn around. Stand in front of the microwave.
Open the microwave. Place the mug on the left side. Close the door. Turn on the microwave for five seconds. Open the door. Take out the mug.
Exit to the right and cross to the right. Go straight ahead. At the end, cross to the right. Enter the cabinet. Turn right.
Open the cabinet. Place the mug to the left, near the edge. Close the cabinet doors.
anns.task_desc: Find a mug, heat it up and strain the cabbage.

high_descs: Turn around and walk right down the passage to enter the room on the right to reach the desk on the right.
Pick up the mug from the table.
Turn around and turn right and find the microwave on the right.
Heat the mug in the microwave and take the mug out.
Turn right and take another right turn at the cabinet and walk down the passage and turn right into the bathroom to face the sink.
Put the mug in the cabinet below the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated Mug in the Cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right and head straight, turn left and then turn right towards the desk
Pick up mug from the desk
Turn around and head straight, turn right and then proceed to turn right and make a turn right towards the microwave
Place mug inside microwave and then take it out
Turn right and head straight, turn right and then proceed to turn right and make a turn left towards the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Heating mug on microwave and placing it in cabinet
